@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vgemho(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v1 + 0.16 * v0 + 0.36)))
    v2 = (tmp + ((v2 + 0.82 - v0 + 0.77) * (tmp + 0.11 / v2 + 0.84)))
    v2 = 0.99
    data[tid] = v0
